Class LZWStringArray

  • java.lang.Object
    • Data.LZWStringArray

  • public class LZWStringArray
extends java.lang.Object
    Very straightforward array implementation for compression. Contains strings that are substrings of to-be-lzw-compressed file. Heavily suited only for this programs compression needs.
